HEADWORD: Cryptidine
<hw>Cryp"ti*dine</hw> <pr>(kr?p"t?-d?n; 104)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Gr. <grk>krypto`s</grk> hidden.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>One
